Name: Average time for Accepted + Wait across all process variants
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Total time spent in Accepted + Wait per case
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Minimum time required to complete Accepted + Wait after its initiation
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Accepted + Wait and the end of the case

Name: Time elapsed from the start of a case until Accepted + Wait is first performed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Time between Accepted + In Progress and Accepted + Wait
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + In Progress' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Time between Accepted + Wait and Completed + Resolved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Cycle time of Accepted + Wait when followed by Completed + Resolved
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Duration of Accepted + Wait in variants that also contain Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Duration of Accepted + Wait in variants that do not contain Completed + In Call
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call does not occur

Name: Time difference between Accepted + Wait and Accepted + Wait - User
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Time difference between Accepted + Wait and Accepted + Wait - Implementation
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Implementation'

Name: Time difference between Accepted + Wait and Accepted + Wait - Vendor
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - Vendor'

Name: Time from Queued + Awaiting Assignment to Accepted + Wait
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Time from Accepted + Assigned to Accepted + Wait
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Assigned' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Elapsed time between the end of Accepted + Wait and the start of Completed + Closed
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Closed'

Name: Time it takes to resume processing after Accepted + Wait (i.e., time from Accepted + Wait to next non-wait activity)
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Duration of Accepted + Wait in cases where Completed + In Call appears before it
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Duration of Accepted + Wait in cases where Completed + In Call appears after it
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and the end of case where activity 'Completed + In Call occurs

Name: Time between consecutive occurrences of Accepted + Wait within the same case
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Accepted + Wait' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'

Name: Time from case creation to the completion of Accepted + Wait
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment' and activity 'Accepted + Wait'
